latestIgtvVideos.title: Casa Bacardi @ home!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’m back behind the bar just for @bacardi 🤍
Join me this Saturday (10th Oct), 4 pm onwards for Casa Bacardi @ home for performances, workshops, pop ups etc. 
Leading up to it, I tried a super easy cocktail with just 3 simple🍹 ingredients
Bacardi Carta Blanca, pineapple juice & coconut milk. 
So I’m Challenging @awokaawomi @cheekoo @rod.anker
to create their own Bacardi cocktails or do what moves them!
To experience the digital festival head on to @lemonade_social @homegrownin 
#dowhatmovesyou #casabacardi

latestIgtvVideos.title: I’m a routine hag. Simple Skin care routine ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I follow a super easy skin routine considering I have super sensitive & acne prone skin. All my teen years I battled with shitty skin and tried all kinds of home remedies (which made it worse lol) it’s certainly not perfect now but with a lot of trial and error I’ve found something that works for me also changing my food habits and lifestyle has helped. 
BTW missed out a major product I use before bed. BENZAC AC 2.5% (consult with your dermatologist)
